{"article_id":"fxRGE0BrTzsYVqVU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump announced Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"that conditions have been met between Turkey and the Kurdish-led Syrian Democratic Forces","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"( SDF )","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"for what he called a `` permanent ceasefire '' between the two sides","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"and that the United States is lifting sanctions on Ankara","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"that were implemented","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"following the invasion of northern Syria .","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"Speaking at the White House ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"while a `` permanent ceasefire '' will be tough to maintain in the volatile region ,","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"he hopes","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"it will last","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"and end the conflict between Turkey and the Kurds .","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"`` I do believe","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"it will be permanent , ''","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"`` This was an outcome","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"created by us , the United States , and nobody else ...","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"we 've done something very , very special . '' 'PERMANENT ' TURKEY-SYRIA CEASE-FIRE POSSIBLE","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"AS TEMPORARY PEACE AGREEMENT ENDS ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"PENCE SAYS","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Trump delivered the statement amid bipartisan criticism over his recent decision","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to pull back U.S. forces from northern Syria ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"opening the door for Turkey to launch a military offensive .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"But the administration has sought to halt the fighting .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"The ceasefire required Kurdish forces","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"formerly allied with the U.S. against the Islamic State group","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to move out of a roughly 20-mile zone on the Turkish border .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"With Kurdish forces out of the zone , Turkey will halt its assault ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"`` We 've saved the lives of many , many Kurds , ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Trump added","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"if Turkey breaches the cease-fire ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"the sanctions could be reimposed .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"`` The sanctions are lifted","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"unless something happens","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that we 're not happy with , ''","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Trump 's statement follows an early morning tweet ,","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"where he announced a \" safe zone \" along the Turkey-Syria border ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"and voiced optimism","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"after the initial 120-hour pause in the Turkish military operation there ended .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"\" Ceasefire has held","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"and combat missions have ended .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Kurds are safe","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"and have worked very nicely with us , \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"\" Captured ISIS prisoners secured . \"","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"The U.S. withdrawal was followed immediately by Turkish aggression ,","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"and Trump faced criticism from Democrats and Republicans alike","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"who blamed him for allowing the violence to go unchecked","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"and leaving Kurdish allies to fend for themselves .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Turkey and Russia reached an agreement Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"that would transform the map of northeast Syria ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"installing their forces along the border","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"and filling the void","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"left by the abrupt withdrawal of U.S. troops .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Trump said Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"that nearly all U.S. troops will be leaving Syria","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"but some will remain","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"to safeguard oil fields in Syria .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Russian forces have already begun joint patrols with Turkish forces along the Turkish-Syrian border .","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan met with Vice President Pence and Secretary of State Mike Pompeo in Ankara last week","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"to work out the initial cease-fire .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Though that period has since lapsed ,","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Pence said earlier","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"there 's an opportunity for a permanent cease-fire in the region .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"James Jeffrey , a career diplomat","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"who oversees Washington ' s role in the global fight against the Islamic State ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"also told lawmakers on the Senate Foreign Relations Committee","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"that he does not believe","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"the troop withdrawal added to Turkey ' s decision","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"to invade northern Syria .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Jeffrey , however , did concede","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"if U.S. forces had been told to stand their ground amid a Turkish invasion ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Turkey may have thought otherwise about crossing the border .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"IRAQ 'S MILITARY SAYS","depth":3},{"id":81,"text":"US TROOPS","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"LEAVING SYRIA","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"DO N'T HAVE PERMISSION","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"TO STAY IN THE COUNTRY","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"Under the recent 10-point deal , Russia and Turkey have given Kurdish fighters 150 hours","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"starting at noon Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"- meaning , until next Tuesday at 6 p.m. -","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"to withdraw from the border .","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"Russian and Syrian government forces would move into that area immediately","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"to ensure","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"the Kurdish fighters pull back 20 miles from the border .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Then at the end of the 150 hours , Russian-Turkish patrols would begin along a six-mile-wide strip of the border .","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"The exception would be the region around the town of Qamishli at the far eastern end of the border ,","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"which has some of the densest Kurdish population .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Russian spokesperson Dmitry Peskov said ,","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"according to Russian newswires ,","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"if the Kurds do not complete their withdrawal by the Tuesday deadline ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Turkey would resume their offensive .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"\" It ' s quite obvious that","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"if the Kurdish units don ' t withdraw with their weapons","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"then Syrian border guards and Russian military police will have to step back .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"And the remaining Kurdish units will be steamrolled by the Turkish army , ''","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"Peskov said .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":184,"right":208,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":184,"left":159,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":155,"right":158,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":145,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":129,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":